DESCRIPTOR.STUDY_TITLE: Korean Lung Cancer - 36 pair WES data
DESCRIPTOR.STUDY_ABSTRACT: This study includes 36 paired samples of Korean Lung Cancer paitients.36 Lung Cnacer samples are paired with each normal(Saliva derived for control) sequencing data.The results of this WES study were analyzed by Mutect and GATK for ranking germline variants and cancer variants to make mutational profile matrix.
